revision.text:
'''Une histoire d'eau'''(aka A Story of Water) is a film directed and written by [[Jean-Luc Godard]]
and [[François Truffaut]] in 1961.  It recounts the story of a woman's trip to Paris, which is surrounded by a large flooded area.

